Package: rayballer
Type: Package
Title: Raytrace Spheres
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2019-02-24
Author: Tyler Morgan-Wall
Maintainer: Tyler Morgan-Wall <tylermw@gmail.com>
Description: A raytracer for lambertian, metallic, and dielectric spheres. Uses a tidy `tibble` input to build scenes. Based off of Peter Shirley's "Raytracing in One Weekend".
License: GPL (>= 2)
